---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="relative py-32 px-6"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-cyan-500/20 bg-cyan-500/5 text-cyan-400 mb-4">
        Sobre mí
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
        <span class="gradient-cyan-purple">Resumen Profesional</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-lg text-default leading-relaxed">
            Soy <strong class="text-primary">Ezequiel Flores</strong>, QA Automation Engineer y Frontend Developer con experiencia en la creación de sistemas de pruebas automatizadas y desarrollo de interfaces modernas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-offset leading-relaxed">
            Combino habilidades en <strong class="text-primary">Playwright</strong>, <strong class="text-primary">Cypress</strong> y <strong class="text-primary">Vue.js</strong> para entregar productos confiables y funcionales. He implementado pruebas E2E, smoke tests y regression tests en sistemas productivos reales, aplicando patrones como Page Object Model para mantener suites escalables y mantenibles.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-2">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-sm">
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse" />
              Disponible para oportunidades laborales
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl glass flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="logomark" class="h-24 text-cyan-400/80" />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-lg">
              QA
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
